# Supplier Environment Variables

## Development (.env.local)

```env
# API Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3001

# App Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=NileLink Supplier Hub
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3002

# Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_NOTIFICATIONS=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true

# Auth
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_PROVIDER=firebase
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_firebase_api_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project.firebaseapp.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
```

## Production (.env.production)

```env
# API Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.nilelink.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://api.nilelink.app

# App Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=NileLink Supplier Hub
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://supplier.nilelink.app

# Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_NOTIFICATIONS=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true

# Auth (Production)
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_PROVIDER=firebase
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=production_firebase_api_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=nilelink.firebaseapp.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=nilelink_prod

# Sentry (Error Tracking)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://your_sentry_dsn@sentry.io/project_id

# Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
```

## Cloudflare Pages Configuration

Add these in Cloudflare Pages dashboard under Environment Variables:

1. **NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL**: https://api.nilelink.app
2. **NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL**: https://supplier.nilelink.app
3. **NODE_VERSION**: 18.17.0
4. **NEXT_PUBLIC_ENV**: production

